OpenSign Darija includes integration code and metadata for public dataset sources.

Mendeley Data: "A Dataset for Moroccan Sign Language (MoSL)", Version 1, DOI
10.17632/23phgyt3mt.1, by FATIMA BEN ZAID, Mohamed BENADDY, and Abdelbasset BOUKDIR,
licensed CC BY 4.0.

Related ScienceDirect article DOI 10.1016/j.dib.2025.112395 is treated as documentation
for the same Mendeley dataset, not as a duplicate data source.

The Kaggle Moroccan Sign Language alphabet dataset is registered but disabled until its
license is verified from official Kaggle metadata.
